374
00:20:38,546 --> 00:20:42,752
Oh, you're on in five minutes, so tune
up your guitar, get your voice ready.

375
00:20:42,785 --> 00:20:44,586
Are you excited? I'm excited.

376
00:20:44,619 --> 00:20:47,489
- Yeah, yeah.
- Hailey Mays is in the building.

377
00:20:47,522 --> 00:20:49,859
Yeah, she is.

378
00:20:52,728 --> 00:20:56,098
[applause]

379
00:20:56,132 --> 00:20:58,067
Hey, folks. Okay.

380
00:20:58,100 --> 00:21:02,939
Uh, now, we got a wonderful new
singer here named Hailey Mays.

381
00:21:02,972 --> 00:21:06,842
And, uh, tonight, Hailey's gonna
sing an original composition.

382
00:21:06,876 --> 00:21:09,544
